                "sidebar_heading": "Advice and Rules",
                "image": {
                    "type": "image",
                    "name": "Advice and Rules",
                    "image": "Sidebar_1_AdviceAndRules.png"
                },
                "html": "A harrow doll\u2019s box container usually has a coin slot for customers to pay for divinations. The price for a harrow doll to cast augury is typically 1 sp. Harrow dolls can also cast locate for a price of 5 gp."
